{"word":"Elkanah","slug":"elkanah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Elkanah</b> <a href=\"#/H511\">H511</a> <br/> 1. Grandson of Korah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=24'>Exo 6:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=23'>1Ch 6:23</a><br/> 2. Father of Samuel; a descendant of preceding<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=1'>1Sa 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=4'>1Sa 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=8'>1Sa 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=19'>1Sa 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=21'>1Sa 1:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=23'>1Sa 1:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=11'>1Sa 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=20'>1Sa 2:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=27'>1Ch 6:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=34'>1Ch 6:34</a><br/> 3. A Levite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=25'>1Ch 6:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=36'>1Ch 6:36</a><br/> 4. Possibly identical with a Levite above<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=26'>1Ch 6:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=35'>1Ch 6:35</a><br/> 5. A Levite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=16'>1Ch 9:16</a><br/> 6. A Levite who joined David at Ziklag<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=6'>1Ch 12:6</a><br/> 7. A doorkeeper for the ark, perhaps identical with the Levite who joined David at Ziklag above<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=23'>1Ch 15:23</a><br/> 8. A prince of Ahaz<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=7'>2Ch 28:7</a>"}]}